{"tid":654353,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【屯門新盤】御半山首日錄逾1,000入票 超額認購7倍","createTime":"2018-05-05T14:33:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-05T15:05:29.000Z","uid":68476,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"f370c2466a6caa388b8c6cd8c2832b129518fb3f","tid":654353,"uid":68476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T14:33:12.000Z","msg":"【屯門新盤】御半山首日錄逾1,000入票 超額認購7倍<br />\n<br />\n新地（016）代理業務部總經理張卓秀敏表示，旗下屯門新盤御半山最快日內加推，仍在商討提價幅度，最快下周末作首輪開售。她指，該盤今日首日開放示範單位及收票，首四個鐘已經錄得逾5,000人次參觀，預料今日全日錄逾萬人次參觀，較預期理想。<br />\n<br />\n市場消息指，御半山首日錄約1,040張入票登記，以首批118伙計，超額認購7.8倍。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180505/large/1525525137_a0fe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180505%2Flarge%2F1525525137_a0fe.jpg&h=8a0d5ddc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c9870d53d1d675e39589b569fe587bb8275db8dc","tid":654353,"uid":53484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T14:56:24.000Z","msg":"CLS"},{"pid":"d68dab04f53f6d3c23060b765e254b783ff387d1","tid":654353,"uid":52946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T14:59:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee4d265eed05886f292674d0a7fba0b7f375c87b","tid":654353,"uid":44851,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T15:02:26.000Z","msg":"不問價入幾手先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a5d3effa90b4abdb5afc308ee084c0efb58d980","tid":654353,"uid":96486,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T15:05:26.000Z","msg":"購買力咁強，樓價會有機會跌？我唔信了"},{"pid":"8ef924b909950ab20b73fea34e571020a3fa78dd","tid":654353,"uid":40089,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T15:05:29.000Z","msg":"幾多水份票都未知啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}